
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
Without words we&#8217;ll meet somewhere<br />
We&#8217;ll keep going hand in hand<br />
As if many years didn&#8217;t pass by</p>
<p>Without words, without questions and without lies<br />
We&#8217;ll find a piece of dream<br />
That lives at the bottom of the heart all the time</p>
<p>Giving my inner self<br />
You only know it, you understand it<br />
Let&#8217;s not pretend for a moment<br />
Without words, without lies</p>
<p>Devotedly we&#8217;ll separate without words in the morning<br />
With eternal wish, that again<br />
We may in a house of dream<br />
Find our port</p>
